{
  "stem": "13623.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Allies used to come through with hundreds of planes going on bombing missions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] They had two ways of-- the siren had two ways of letting us know when the planes are approaching was like three long blasts.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when the planes were like overhead, they had like a-- a crying, wailing blasting of the-- of the sirens.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we knew the planes were far-- further yet or we knew the planes are already almost on top of us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They must have known the camp, because they never bombed the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they bombed the railroad siding and the land outside of the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the barracks are so thin that when they were bombing, the barracks would vibrate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first time this ever happened, we never had any experience with bombing and-- and that kind of situation, we all-- when-- we all sort of hid under the beds as-- as if this would save us.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We could not go-- get out of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were all-- it was dark out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It had to be a blackout.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the orders from the SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But because it was-- it was a-- a very dreary time, especially the first time this happened, we heard the explosions of the bombs.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were all like crouching under the-- under the beds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was as quiet as a-- you could hear a pin drop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody was just having their own thoughts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES] One of the guys started to sing 'My Yiddishe Momme,' just-- he broke the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [DRINKS] [SIGHS] he broke the silence.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] [SIGHING] That song, I've heard that song sung many times after.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that song, that time really hit everybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
